284
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:17,342
My life's just been a succession of jams
over floozies of one kind or another.

285
00:36:18,343 --> 00:36:20,387
I forget how to treat a real lady.

286
00:36:23,139 --> 00:36:25,600
What do you say
we forget about the whole thing?

287
00:36:25,725 --> 00:36:27,769
Start over. Make friends.

288
00:36:33,191 --> 00:36:36,778
How about tonight? Wanna go for a ride?

289
00:36:38,071 --> 00:36:42,534
Hey, look... I have to get back.

290
00:36:44,828 --> 00:36:46,871
I'll drive you.

291
00:36:47,956 --> 00:36:51,459
- It's just walking distance.
- I'll walk you.

292
